{
  "stem": "21582.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there they see this awful looking group of-- of people that looked like skeletons with these bulging eyes and some shaved and-- and skinny.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, oh, what is that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Jews.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were so repulsive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And so we were taunted on the way with-- you know, we were taunted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- you would think that the Polish people suffered a great, great deal during the war, that there would be some-- some identification and some-- some compassion, but very little.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I certainly did not encounter any, neither did my sister or my mother, or the people in my group.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we found, finally, a place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just-- just-- there was also a curfew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we knew that we had to find shelter before-- before dark fell.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you know that in the winter, dusk, dark is-- is much earlier.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We found a building, a school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and we stayed in-- in that school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We lived in a closet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In a-- we used the shelf.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was-- it was a scholar-- a closet for school supplies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we used-- we used this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then from there we still felt we want to move, either find other relatives or go and find these two cousins.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We wanted to-- to latch onto something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were so helpless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- we knew that we had relatives who lived before the war in a town that is called Kielce that was not too awful far from Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it-- and it was on the way to where my cousins lived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so we were moved-- we-- we-- whether we went on a train-- I think we went-- we-- we got on a train.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
